{"tid":1815234,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周子瑜回台了！投下人生第一張選票？他驚喊投票率恐暴漲！","createTime":"2020-01-07T11:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T12:29:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"20efff268ce989ea702b8fd725d409b2235bd4fe","tid":1815234,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VOLLB77qV2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVOLLB77qV2Q&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=1e8143ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VOLLB77qV2Q</a><br />\n2020大選倒數最後4天，而農曆春節也即將到來，不少居住國外的台灣人紛紛回台。據韓國娛樂新聞報導，韓團TWICE成員周子瑜今（7）日搭機返回台灣。消息一傳出，台灣網友紛紛表示期待，能在投票所巧遇「首投族」周子瑜；因此，就有人笑稱，今年年輕人的投票率恐怕要大漲了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZezryW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZezryW3.jpg&h=cc409847&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n▲ 周子瑜今日現身機場，準備搭機返台。<br />\n<br />\n根據韓國娛樂新聞Newsen報導，周子瑜今日在相關人員的陪同下，低調地現身機場，只見她壓低帽緣，穿著黃色毛衣，帶著一副遮住半臉的圓框眼鏡，心情看起來相當輕鬆，不停地和旁人有說有笑。此外，現場粉絲上前關心，「是不是要回台灣投票」，周子瑜面露微笑，但沒有正面回答。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymAqPvx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymAqPvx.jpg&h=892a8263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲ 針對周子瑜此番回台，網友戲稱大選投票率恐怕會大漲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qPK43S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qPK43S.jpg&h=98d8117a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1999年6月出生的周子瑜，至今剛好滿20歲，也是第一次擁有投票的機會。由於台灣大選將至，她這次的返台讓人臆測紛紛。有網友在 PTT以「子瑜回家投票？？」為題發文指出，「真．北漂青年子瑜，今天竟然搭機回台灣了。剛好子瑜今年滿20歲，該不會休假順便回來投票吧？也就是說，台南人投票時，排在你前面的可能是子瑜？」<br />\n<br />\n文章一出，立刻引來大批網友留言表示期待，「這才是真正催票啊」、「年輕人投票率要上漲30%了」、「子瑜都回來投票了！你各位還在耍嘴皮」、「投票所會爆滿吧」。不過，也有人認為，「提早回來過年吧」、「正常行程而已，每年過年前TWICE都會休假各自回家」。<br />\n<br />\n奶共公司JYP實要佢投韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcd2b73ec79e96cd75e376b39712d9daf364223","tid":1815234,"uid":256952,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"佢一定投韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c483b26d35761501fc403fbd643c038f2bc438dc","tid":1815234,"uid":213300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"投自己定投小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4d41a3cb06a6fe659b2a5e4fa9b6e73e14d91b","tid":1815234,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c483b26d35761501fc403fbd643c038f2bc438dc","tid":1815234,"uid":213300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"投自己定投小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"投ENGLISH會唔會比國內同胞屌"},{"pid":"df83cf5f25c604c140f24be1c5881e9c84b55d0a","tid":1815234,"uid":224479,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"張相影到好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951ddd19bd4f662c0f2e11b5e10d8de9eb01e2f2","tid":1815234,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6b4d41a3cb06a6fe659b2a5e4fa9b6e73e14d91b","tid":1815234,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c483b26d35761501fc403fbd643c038f2bc438dc","tid":1815234,"uid":213300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"投自己定投小英<img src=\"/assets/faces